{"title":"JS - 面向对象","date":"2019-10-14T10:06:51.195Z","link":"2019/10/14/js-面向对象","tags":["JS"],"updated":"2019-10-15T09:10:15.030Z","content":"<h2 id=\"概念\">概念<a href=\"2019/10/14/js-面向对象#概念\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li>类，即模板</li>\n<li>对象（实例）</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"面向对象三要素\">面向对象三要素<a href=\"2019/10/14/js-面向对象#面向对象三要素\"></a></h2><ol>\n<li>继承，子类继承父类</li>\n<li>封装<br> 减少耦合，保护数据，接口的权限管理。</li>\n<li>多态，同一接口不同实现<br> 保持子类开放性和灵活性，面向接口编程</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"实例\">实例<a href=\"2019/10/14/js-面向对象#实例\"></a></h2><h5 id=\"jQuery是怎么面向对象的\">jQuery是怎么面向对象的<a href=\"2019/10/14/js-面向对象#jQuery是怎么面向对象的\"></a></h5><figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">class jQuery &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    constructor(selector)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\"># Array.prototype.slice 方法将伪数组转为数组</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">let</span> dom = Array.prototype.slice.call(document.querySelectorAll(selector))</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">let</span> len = dom ? dom.length : 0</span><br><span class=\"line\">        </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">for</span> ( <span class=\"built_in\">let</span> i = 0; i &lt; len; i++ ) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            this [i]  = dom [i]</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        this.length = len</span><br><span class=\"line\">        this.selector = selector</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    append (node) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    addClass (name) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\"># 此处省略n个api...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">window.$ = <span class=\"keyword\">function</span> (selector) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">return</span> new jQuery(selector)</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"面向对象的意义\">面向对象的意义<a href=\"2019/10/14/js-面向对象#面向对象的意义\"></a></h2><p>数据结构化</p>\n","prev":{"title":"五大设计原则（SOLID）","link":"2019/10/15/设计模式/设计原则"},"next":{"title":"JS 设计模式","link":"2019/10/12/设计模式/设计模式"},"plink":"yibaobeiya.github.io/2019/10/14/js-面向对象/","toc":[{"title":"概念","id":"概念","index":"1"},{"title":"面向对象三要素","id":"面向对象三要素","index":"2"},{"title":"实例","id":"实例","index":"3"},{"title":"面向对象的意义","id":"面向对象的意义","index":"4"}]}